Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 4.0.0), ant (>= 1.7.0), ant-optional (>= 1.7.0), sun-java6-jdk|java6-sdk, open-xchange-drive (>= @OXVERSION@), open-xchange-grizzly (>= @OXVERSION@)
Standards-Version: 3.8.4
Homepage: http://www.open-xchange.com

Package: open-xchange-drive-comet
Architecture: all
Pre-Depends: open-xchange-core (>= @OXVERSION@)
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, open-xchange-drive (>= @OXVERSION@), open-xchange-grizzly (>= @OXVERSION@)
Description: Drive push implementation using Comet and using less system resources
 This package should be installed if a real push implementation for the drive synchronization is wanted. This push implementation uses less
 system resources by using the Grizzly application server which allows freeing threads although the request is still active.
